(293, 0, '2020-08-12 04:30:05', '2020-08-12 04:30:05', 'Growing up in Indonesia in the shadow of an active volcano, Agus Haryono has witnessed the deadly risks of living in a disaster-prone region. This prompted him to join the country’s Search and Rescue Agency, in the hope of saving lives, when disaster strikes.', 'Real Life Heroes: heading into disaster, in the service of others', 'Growing up in Indonesia in the shadow of an active volcano, Agus Haryono has witnessed the deadly risks of living in a disaster-prone region. This prompted him to join the country’s Search and Rescue Agency, in the hope of saving lives, when disaster strikes.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'real-life-heroes-heading-into-disaster-in-the-service-of-others', '', '', '2020-08-12 04:30:05', '2020-08-12 04:30:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost/HRnews.local/?post_type=wprss_feed_item&p=293', 0, 'wprss_feed_item', '', 0),
