(534, 2, '2020-09-12 14:27:56', '2020-09-12 04:27:56', '<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">GHRD focuses on the rights of minorities in South Asia.</p>\n<p>Any individual victim of human rights violations, the legal representative of a victim, or a human rights defender can submit complaints of potential human rights violations committed in South Asia by using the form below.</p>\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">Please ensure that each message contains:<br />– The victim(s) name and date of birth<br />– Your name and relationship to the victim(s)<br />– A detailed summary of the facts in chronological order<br />– Any relevant details regarding the local authorities approached – such as the police or local court system</p>\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">The information provided <strong>must not</strong> be based on reports exclusively disseminated in the mass media.</p>\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">Our Human Rights legal department will assess this complaint and contact you if we would like more information.</p>\n\n<!-- wp:gravityforms/form {\"formId\":\"1\",\"ajax\":true} /-->', 'Submit a Violation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '487-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-12 14:27:56', '2020-09-12 04:27:56', '', 487, 'https://news.saras.care/487-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
