rass and persecute the lawyers who defend opposition activists and human rights.”</p>', 'Bahrain: Lawyers Prosecuted on Speech Charges', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '828-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-13 22:29:13', '2020-09-13 12:29:13', '', 828, 'https://news.saras.care/828-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
